channel.title: Error - Unknown Identifier
channel.description:
Right, I've got this error:
[code]Line 54: [Error] (14593:1): Unknown identifier 'DropTo' in script D:\Program Files\SCAR 3.15\Scripts\My Scripts\Power Fisher.scar[/code]
and the part where it's getting the error is:
[code] procedure DropIt;
begin
DropTo(2-28);
end;[/code]
I've read a part about this error in a tutorial, but that doesn't help me. Any help would be greatly appreciated.
Thanks, R1ch4

item.title: Error - Unknown Identifier
item.dc:creator: @IP-Drowner IP-Drowner
item.description:
@IP-Drowner wrote:

[quote=“Nashi, post:4, topic:221490”]By the looks of the script, It’s fairly old, Now, Correct me if I’m wrong Dan
But I think DropTo was changed to DropToPosition, and it should be DropToPosition(2,28);[/quote]
DropTo and DropToPosition have been taken out of SRL since of the 6th revision (i think). You can still add your own one, such as:procedure DropTo(SP, EP: Integer); //Created by Dan's The Man (a.k.a IP-Drowner/Daniel) var i: Integer; begin for i:=SP to EP do if(ExistsItem(i)) then DropItem(i); end;
